        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks AG for references about phyllotaxy</p>
            <p>and information on marriage laws.</p> 
<p>Has been looking for dimorphism in <hi rend="italic">Phlox</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Euonymus</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has observed the irritability of tendrils of <hi rend="italic">Echinocystis</hi> with great interest. Was also struck by the rotating movements of the leading shoots, which he proposes to investigate.</p> 
        </abstract>
